<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>国土报最新头条</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 23 Nov 2023 18:08:28 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>“作为四个男孩的以色列母亲，军队游戏不是我想玩的”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/holylandings/2023-11-23/ty-article/.highlight/as-an-israeli-mother-of-four-boys-the-army-game-is-not-something-i-want-to-play/0000018b-fd25-d99b-a7eb-fdb77c2d0000</link><description>本周在本古里安机场：战争愈演愈烈，一位母亲担心孩子的未来，一对俄罗斯夫妇逃离另一个冲突地区</description><pubDate>Thu, 23 Nov 2023 17:29:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/holylandings/2023-11-23/ty-article/.highlight/as-an-israeli-mother-of-four-boys-the-army-game-is-not-something-i-want-to-play/0000018b-fd25-d99b-a7eb-fdb77c2d0000</guid></item><item><title>导致灾难的不是加沙脱离接触，而是内塔尼亚胡的政策</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-23/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/it-wasnt-the-gaza-disengagement-but-netanyahus-policies-that-led-to-disaster/0000018b-fcf1-de73-a9bb-fef7ab240000</link><description>追寻10月7日惨案的历史根源，我们必须回到十年前总理的决定</description><pubDate>Thu, 23 Nov 2023 17:04:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-23/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/it-wasnt-the-gaza-disengagement-but-netanyahus-policies-that-led-to-disaster/0000018b-fcf1-de73-a9bb-fef7ab240000</guid></item><item><title>西方外交官：加沙“处于医疗灾难的边缘”，有疾病爆发的迹象</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2023-11-23/ty-article/.premium/western-diplomats-gaza-on-the-verge-of-medical-catastrophe-signs-of-disease-outbreak/0000018b-fc8c-d330-a9bb-ffdeafe70000</link><description>几位接受《国土报》采访的外交官报告称，近东救济工程处警告称，儿童皮肤病爆发，胃肠道疾病病例有所增加。一位外交官警告说，加沙的医疗系统正在崩溃。 “如果发生这种情况，以色列也会受到伤害”</description><pubDate>Thu, 23 Nov 2023 16:36:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2023-11-23/ty-article/.premium/western-diplomats-gaza-on-the-verge-of-medical-catastrophe-signs-of-disease-outbreak/0000018b-fc8c-d330-a9bb-ffdeafe70000</guid></item><item><title>华盛顿自由派领导人警告说，保守派在加沙战争问题上让年轻的民主党人失望了</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-11-23/ty-article-magazine/.premium/young-democrats-are-being-failed-by-the-old-guard-warns-leading-d-c-liberal/0000018b-fc5e-d330-a9bb-ffded9a60000</link><description>美国进步中心主席帕特里克·加斯帕德告诉《国土报》，为什么对以色列-加沙战争的反应需要给民主党人敲响警钟，他们正在驳斥千禧一代和 Z 世代的观点。内塔尼亚胡本人对以色列的看法，”他说</description><pubDate>Thu, 23 Nov 2023 16:36:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-11-23/ty-article-magazine/.premium/young-democrats-are-being-failed-by-the-old-guard-warns-leading-d-c-liberal/0000018b-fc5e-d330-a9bb-ffded9a60000</guid></item><item><title>以色列与哈马斯的战争已经蔓延到纽约的烹饪界</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-23/ty-article/.premium/the-israel-hamas-war-has-spilled-into-n-y-c-s-cuisine-scene/0000018b-fc6c-d330-a9bb-fffeb1540000</link><description>纽约市的以色列餐馆正面临抵制、反以色列涂鸦和在线分享“犹太复国主义餐馆”地点的呼声。以色列餐馆老板声称他们没有被吓倒</description><pubDate>Thu, 23 Nov 2023 16:30:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-23/ty-article/.premium/the-israel-hamas-war-has-spilled-into-n-y-c-s-cuisine-scene/0000018b-fc6c-d330-a9bb-fffeb1540000</guid></item><item><title>对于埃及来说，其在以色列与哈马斯谈判中的作用事关国家安全</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-23/ty-article/.premium/for-egypt-its-role-in-israel-hamas-negotiations-is-a-matter-of-national-security/0000018b-fc26-d783-a3df-fc3e312e0000</link><description>埃及担心，临时停火后加沙地带南部战火重燃，将导致加沙人大规模移民埃及。除了外交努力外，埃及军队正在加强边境，以防止这种情况发生</description><pubDate>Thu, 23 Nov 2023 16:18:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-23/ty-article/.premium/for-egypt-its-role-in-israel-hamas-negotiations-is-a-matter-of-national-security/0000018b-fc26-d783-a3df-fc3e312e0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列逮捕加沙Al-Shifa主任：“监督医院被用作哈马斯总部”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-23/ty-article/.premium/israel-arrests-director-of-gazas-al-shifa-oversaw-hospitals-use-as-hamas-hq/0000018b-fccf-d4d0-addf-ffff02850000</link><description>据以色列军方称，哈马斯利用医院的许多资源来运营其在大楼下建造的隧道系统。以色列国防军国际发言人表示，以色列带他只是为了“问几个问题”</description><pubDate>Thu, 23 Nov 2023 16:11:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-23/ty-article/.premium/israel-arrests-director-of-gazas-al-shifa-oversaw-hospitals-use-as-hamas-hq/0000018b-fccf-d4d0-addf-ffff02850000</guid></item><item><title>英国政府发言人在英国电视台表示，以色列人质和巴勒斯坦囚犯之间没有同等性</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-23/ty-article/no-equivalence-between-israeli-hostages-and-palestinian-prisoners-says-govt-spokesperson/0000018b-fc9b-d8d0-a58f-ffdb88fe0000</link><description>天空新闻主持人指责以色列没有像以色列人那样重视巴勒斯坦人的生命，因为交换比例为 3:1。政府发言人艾隆·利维（Eylon Levy）：“这是一项令人震惊的指控，如果我们可以为每一名人质释放一名囚犯，我们显然会这么做”</description><pubDate>Thu, 23 Nov 2023 16:07:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-23/ty-article/no-equivalence-between-israeli-hostages-and-palestinian-prisoners-says-govt-spokesperson/0000018b-fc9b-d8d0-a58f-ffdb88fe0000</guid></item><item><title>周五下午，13 名以色列妇女和儿童将从加沙哈马斯的囚禁中获释</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-23/ty-article/.premium/13-israeli-women-and-children-to-be-released-from-hamas-captivity-in-gaza-on-friday/0000018b-fcad-de73-a9bb-feefe4150000</link><description>卡塔尔外交部发言人证实，以色列与哈马斯战争将于周五上午 7 点开始停火，下午 4 点将释放被哈马斯囚禁的 13 名以色列妇女和儿童</description><pubDate>Thu, 23 Nov 2023 15:26:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-23/ty-article/.premium/13-israeli-women-and-children-to-be-released-from-hamas-captivity-in-gaza-on-friday/0000018b-fcad-de73-a9bb-feefe4150000</guid></item><item><title>视频显示加沙 Al-Shifa 医院下哈马斯隧道的确切路径</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2023-11-23/ty-article-magazine/.premium/videos-show-exact-path-of-hamas-tunnels-under-gazas-al-shifa-hospital/0000018b-fc69-d330-a9bb-ffff49790000</link><description>视觉分析显示 160 米长的哈马斯隧道 - 配有房间、浴室和小厨房、通讯、电力和空调 - 在内科病房和应急发电机大楼下方运行</description><pubDate>Thu, 23 Nov 2023 15:17:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2023-11-23/ty-article-magazine/.premium/videos-show-exact-path-of-hamas-tunnels-under-gazas-al-shifa-hospital/0000018b-fc69-d330-a9bb-ffff49790000</guid></item><item><title>战争，我担心吗？以色列极右翼财政部长似乎并不关心加沙战争成本</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-23/ty-article/.premium/war-me-worry-israels-far-right-finance-minister-seems-unconcerned-about-gaza-war-costs/0000018b-fc72-d473-affb-fdfa95af0000</link><description>加沙战争需要一位负责任的财政部长，确保以色列能够承担费用并保持经济运转。这位极右翼政客还有其他优先事项</description><pubDate>Thu, 23 Nov 2023 14:19:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-23/ty-article/.premium/war-me-worry-israels-far-right-finance-minister-seems-unconcerned-about-gaza-war-costs/0000018b-fc72-d473-affb-fdfa95af0000</guid></item><item><title>“这不再是我的加拿大了。我们正在经历对犹太社区前所未有的攻击”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/americas/2023-11-23/ty-article-magazine/.premium/this-is-not-my-canada-were-experiencing-an-unprecedented-assault-on-jewish-community/0000018b-fbca-d473-affb-fbea01020000</link><description>资深人权斗士凯伦·莫克对加拿大对以色列-哈马斯战争的反应感到绝望。她说，犹太人“对未来感到恐惧、痛苦、焦虑和不确定——更不用说被我们的盟友背叛了”</description><pubDate>Thu, 23 Nov 2023 13:49:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/americas/2023-11-23/ty-article-magazine/.premium/this-is-not-my-canada-were-experiencing-an-unprecedented-assault-on-jewish-community/0000018b-fbca-d473-affb-fbea01020000</guid></item><item><title>关于以色列-哈马斯战争，国会议员需要了解什么</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-11-23/ty-article-opinion/.premium/what-members-of-congress-need-to-know-about-the-israel-hamas-war/0000018b-f759-d55f-a3ff-ff5bd7ac0000</link><description>国会议员必须应对哈马斯史无前例的对以色列人的屠杀以及巴勒斯坦平民遭受的不人道苦难所带来的政策影响，同时双方的不怀好意的行为者也利用苦难来推动危险的偏见和狂热议程。</description><pubDate>Thu, 23 Nov 2023 13:31:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-11-23/ty-article-opinion/.premium/what-members-of-congress-need-to-know-about-the-israel-hamas-war/0000018b-f759-d55f-a3ff-ff5bd7ac0000</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯是否在加沙的 Al-Shifa 医院下运作？隧道之旅不容置疑</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-23/ty-article-magazine/.premium/did-hamas-operate-under-al-shifa-a-tour-of-the-tunnels-leaves-no-room-for-doubt/0000018b-f8c7-d783-a3df-f8df15600000</link><description>以色列记者看到设施下方有一条长达 170 多米的管道。医院的管理人员不可能不知道发生了什么事</description><pubDate>Thu, 23 Nov 2023 12:14:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-23/ty-article-magazine/.premium/did-hamas-operate-under-al-shifa-a-tour-of-the-tunnels-leaves-no-room-for-doubt/0000018b-f8c7-d783-a3df-f8df15600000</guid></item><item><title>德国警方在全国范围内进行了十几次突击行动，镇压哈马斯支持者</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/europe/2023-11-23/ty-article/germany-cracks-down-on-hamas-supporters-in-over-a-dozen-police-raids-countrywide/0000018b-fbb5-dafe-a18f-fbf5c8e80000</link><description>在联邦禁止哈马斯和萨米敦之后，德国警方已开始执行禁令并进一步调查这些组织的存在。德国执法部长表示，我们已发出明确信号，即我们不会容忍任何美化哈马斯针对以色列的野蛮恐怖行为</description><pubDate>Thu, 23 Nov 2023 11:42:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/europe/2023-11-23/ty-article/germany-cracks-down-on-hamas-supporters-in-over-a-dozen-police-raids-countrywide/0000018b-fbb5-dafe-a18f-fbf5c8e80000</guid></item><item><title>也门胡塞武装：他们对以色列的红海贸易构成什么威胁？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-23/ty-article-magazine/.premium/yemens-houthis-what-threat-do-they-pose-to-israels-red-sea-trade/0000018b-fbd4-d330-a9bb-ffd64be20000</link><description>如果胡塞武装不仅开始攻击以色列人拥有的船只，而且还攻击往返以色列的船只，会发生什么？ “海洋世界是敏感的，不稳定的安全环境会产生立竿见影的影响”</description><pubDate>Thu, 23 Nov 2023 11:30:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-23/ty-article-magazine/.premium/yemens-houthis-what-threat-do-they-pose-to-israels-red-sea-trade/0000018b-fbd4-d330-a9bb-ffd64be20000</guid></item><item><title>拜登的困境：加沙四天休战结束后美国想要什么？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-11-23/ty-article/.premium/bidens-dilemma-what-does-u-s-want-when-four-day-truce-ends-in-gaza/0000018b-fb78-dafe-a18f-fb799fec0000</link><description>停火期满后，美国人是否支持以色列和哈马斯恢复战争？达到什么政治目的？如果不是，这与美国一再声明哈马斯不能在战后第二天继续掌权有何相容？</description><pubDate>Thu, 23 Nov 2023 11:16:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-11-23/ty-article/.premium/bidens-dilemma-what-does-u-s-want-when-four-day-truce-ends-in-gaza/0000018b-fb78-dafe-a18f-fb799fec0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列：周五之前不会释放人质；卡塔尔表示即将宣布停火</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-23/ty-article/.premium/israel-no-hostage-release-before-friday-qatar-says-cease-fire-announcement-imminent/0000018b-fb3e-dafe-a18f-fb7f285b0000</link><description>一位熟悉谈判的以色列消息人士告诉《国土报》，协议执行的延迟并不是谈判破裂的结果，而是行政问题造成的。</description><pubDate>Thu, 23 Nov 2023 10:16:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-23/ty-article/.premium/israel-no-hostage-release-before-friday-qatar-says-cease-fire-announcement-imminent/0000018b-fb3e-dafe-a18f-fb7f285b0000</guid></item><item><title>“老人带着孩子，离开他们来吧”：与以色列士兵沿着加沙的逃生路线</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-23/ty-article-magazine/.premium/old-man-with-kids-leave-them-and-come-with-israels-soldiers-along-gazas-escape-route/0000018b-f663-d117-abcf-f7efe85a0000</link><description>数百名流离失所的巴勒斯坦人周日在废墟和爆炸声中向加沙南部游行。扩音器里时不时地传来以色列国防军播音员的声音，要求其中一人退出队列。当居民不服从命令时，以色列国防军士兵向空中开枪。 《国土报》参加了记者参观“人道主义走廊”的活动</description><pubDate>Thu, 23 Nov 2023 09:25:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-23/ty-article-magazine/.premium/old-man-with-kids-leave-them-and-come-with-israels-soldiers-along-gazas-escape-route/0000018b-f663-d117-abcf-f7efe85a0000</guid></item><item><title>人质协议不会带来胜利，因为以色列未来几天将面临紧张局势</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-23/ty-article/.premium/hostage-deal-will-yield-no-victory-laps-as-israel-faces-nerve-racking-days-ahead/0000018b-f8f5-dafe-a18f-fbf50bdd0000</link><description>以色列的风险评估和犹豫主要围绕停火问题。哈马斯领导人辛瓦尔正在争取时间，他承诺寻找并解救更多被加沙其他派系绑架的以色列人</description><pubDate>Thu, 23 Nov 2023 06:50:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-23/ty-article/.premium/hostage-deal-will-yield-no-victory-laps-as-israel-faces-nerve-racking-days-ahead/0000018b-f8f5-dafe-a18f-fbf50bdd0000</guid></item></channel></rss>